### =========================
### TASKFLOW API - TASKS
### =========================

### Listar tarefas
GET https://localhost:7064/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

###

### Criar tarefa válida
POST https://localhost:7064/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Estudar validações",
  "description": "Validando CreateTaskDto com DataAnnotations",
  "priority": "medium"
}

###

### Criar tarefa inválida - título curto
POST https://localhost:7064/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "ab",
  "description": "Esse teste deve retornar erro de validação",
  "priority": "medium"
}

###

### Criar tarefa inválida - título ausente
POST https://localhost:7064/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Esse teste deve retornar erro porque title é obrigatório",
  "priority": "medium"
}

###

### Criar tarefa inválida - prioridade inválida
POST https://localhost:7064/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Teste prioridade inválida",
  "description": "Esse teste deve retornar erro de validação",
  "priority": "urgente"
}

###

### Buscar tarefa por ID existente
GET https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/COLE_UM_ID_REAL_AQUI
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar tarefa com ID inválido
GET https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/999
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar tarefa com ObjectId válido, mas inexistente
GET https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar tarefa existente - dados válidos
PUT https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/COLE_UM_ID_REAL_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Tarefa atualizada com validação",
  "description": "Validando UpdateTaskDto com DataAnnotations",
  "priority": "high"
}

###

### Atualizar tarefa existente - apenas prioridade
PUT https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/COLE_UM_ID_REAL_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": "medium"
}

###

### Atualizar tarefa inválida - título curto
PUT https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/COLE_UM_ID_REAL_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "ab",
  "description": "Esse teste deve retornar erro de validação",
  "priority": "medium"
}

###

### Atualizar tarefa inválida - prioridade inválida
PUT https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/6a20b1350035cb0f0b88d5cb
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": "urgente"
}

###

### Atualizar tarefa inexistente
PUT https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Tarefa inexistente",
  "description": "Esse teste deve retornar 404",
  "priority": "low"
}

###

### Concluir tarefa existente
PATCH https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/COLE_UM_ID_REAL_AQUI/complete
Accept: application/json

###

### Concluir tarefa com ID inválido
PATCH https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/999/complete
Accept: application/json

###

### Concluir tarefa inexistente
PATCH https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000/complete
Accept: application/json

###

### Excluir tarefa existente
DELETE https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/6a20eed0292a78c25bad48cf

###

### Excluir tarefa com ID inválido
DELETE https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/999

###

### Excluir tarefa inexistente
DELETE https://localhost:7064/api/tasks/000000000000000000000000